=What you need=
----

<ul><li>A computer: you may bring your laptop (recommended) or borrow the ones we have in the lab.<ul></ul>

</li><li>A pair of LEDs of any color, an <strong>USB A to mini-B cable</strong>, one push button, an LDR sensor, 3 x 0.5m of solid wire (black, red and any other color), a pair of 150 Ohm resistors and some cutting pliers.**<ul></ul>

</li></ul>

<ul><li>Send an email to aereset@gmail.com saying that you are coming.<ul></ul>

